---
title: Tuscan Roast Vegetable Penne with Lemon‑Parsley Pangrattato & Capers
description: We love roasted veggies. And we love pasta. So then we thought, why not combine the two and get a beautiful bowl of concentrated flavour? With a crunchy topping of irresistible pangrattato to finish it off, there's a lot to love in this delicious dish!

*Unfortunately, this week's spaghetti was in short supply, so we've replaced it with penne. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
